metrics.visualTitle: Avg Duration, First Name, Total Duration and Total Trips by lat and lon

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
  FILTER(
    KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Date'[Date])),
    'Date'[Date] < DATE(2019, 8, 1)
  )

EVALUATE
  TOPN(
    3502,
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'StationInformation'[lat],
      'StationInformation'[lon],
      __DS0FilterTable,
      "Avg_Duration", 'Trips'[Avg Duration],
      "MinName", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('StationInformation'[Name]))),
      "Total_Duration", IGNORE('Trips'[Total Duration]),
      "Total_Trips", IGNORE('Trips'[Total Trips])
    ),
    [Avg_Duration],
    0,
    'StationInformation'[lat],
    1,
    'StationInformation'[lon],
    1
  )

ORDER BY
  [Avg_Duration] DESC, 'StationInformation'[lat], 'StationInformation'[lon]

      ),

      "Total_Trips", 'Trips'[Total Trips],

    'StationInformation'[Name],

  )

ORDER BY

  'StationInformation'[Name],

metrics.visualTitle: Total Duration and Total Trips by Date

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Date'[Date])),
      'Date'[Date] < DATE(2019, 8, 1)
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Date'[Date],
      __DS0FilterTable,
      "Total_Duration", 'Trips'[Total Duration],
      "Total_Trips", 'Trips'[Total Trips]
    )

  VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
  SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
    3500,
    __DS0Core,
    'Date'[Date],
    [Total_Duration],
    [Total_Trips],
    350,
    ,
    ALPHABETICAL,
    ASC,
    105000,
    60
  )

ORDER BY
  'Date'[Date]
